s($,"axn","alf",()=>A.b([A.b_(1,61,"First discovered by the Olmec civilization, chocolate is second to none. A minty blend or fennel seeds and Dried Dates covered in luscious chocolate.","Coconut, Fennels, Sesame Seeds, _Cocoa Powder, Sugar, Flavours, _Food Colour (E-155) & N.N Sweetener.","","assets/images/products/mouth_freshener/arabic/arabic1.png","assets/images/products/mouth_freshener/nutrition/nutrition1.png"),A.b_(2,62,"A chocolaty version of our original Shahi Meva, this is sure to delight any chocolate lover.","Fennel Seeds, Dry Dates, Coconut, Almonds, _Glucose, Sugar, Cocoa Powder, Full Cream _Milk Powder, Food Preservative (E-223), _Permitted Food Colors(E-133, E-155, E-102).","","assets/images/products/mouth_freshener/arabic/arabic2.png","assets/images/products/mouth_freshener/nutrition/nutrition2.png"),A.b_(3,63,"The one that started it all. A classic blend of Fennel Seeds and Areca Nuts.","Fennel Seeds, Betelnut, Menthol, _N.N Sweetener, Natural & Artificial _Flavours.","","assets/images/products/mouth_freshener/arabic/arabic3.png",""),A.b_(4,64,"A sophisticated blend on Roasted Fennel Seeds, Coriander Seeds, Sesame Seeds, Coconut and Dried Dates. Dewaan is a depth of flavor and textures.","Fennel Seeds, Coriander Seeds, Coconut, _Sugar, Sesame Seeds, Dry Dates, Food _Colors (E-133) (E-129) & artificial flavors.","","assets/images/products/mouth_freshener/arabic/arabic4.png","assets/images/products/mouth_freshener/nutrition/nutrition4.png"),A.b_(5,65,"The same great taste that consumers have come to love with Shahi Deluxe. A mouth freshener that can be enjoyed by kids & adults alike.","Fennel Seed, Dry Dates, Cardamom, _Menthol, Natural & Artificial Flavours, _N.N Sweetener.","","assets/images/products/mouth_freshener/arabic/arabic5.png","assets/images/products/mouth_freshener/nutrition/nutrition5.png"),A.b_(6,66,"The perfect blend of Fennel Seeds, Dried Dates and Cardamom seeds. The Original \u201cHerbal\u201d Mouth Freshener provides the perfect balance of flavor and refreshment.","Fennel seeds, Dry Dates, Cardamom, _Menthol, N.N Sweetener, Natural & _Artificial Flavors.","","assets/images/products/mouth_freshener/arabic/arabic6.png",""),A.b_(7,67,"Cardamom has been used since ancient times to tantalize and awaken the tastebuds. Shahi Elaichi focuses on enhancing the natural aroma and taste of whole Cardamom with Cardamom seeds.","Fennel, Dry Dates, Less than 1% N.N Sweetener _Saccharine, Menthol, Natural & Artificial Flavours, _Food Colors FD&C Blue # 1(E-133), FD&C _Yellow # 5 (E-102).","","assets/images/products/mouth_freshener/arabic/arabic7.png",""),A.b_(8,68,"A traditional Herbal Mouth Freshener with the added power and benefits of black seeds to give you an immune boost while satisfying your tastebuds.","Nigella Seeds, Fennel Seeds, Cardamom, Dry Dates, _Wheat Flour, Misri, Sugar, & FoodColors (E-102), (E-171), _FD&C Blue #1 (E-133), FD&C Yellow # 5 (E-102).","","assets/images/products/mouth_freshener/arabic/arabic8.png","assets/images/products/mouth_freshener/nutrition/nutrition8.png"),A.b_(9,69,"For those looking for a little sweetness in their Pan Masala, AasPas Meetha Pan Masala, provides the perfect amount of sweetness.","Coconut, Fennels, Coriander Seeds, _Sesame Seeds, Sugar, Menthol, Wheat _Flour, Colours (E-171), (E-102), (E-110), _(E-133), (E-127).","","assets/images/products/mouth_freshener/arabic/arabic9.png","assets/images/products/mouth_freshener/nutrition/nutrition9.png"),A.b_(10,70,"A sweet and nutty mixture of nature\u2019s goodness. Shahi Meva is the perfect treat to satisfy your sweet tooth with a hint of vanilla, Almonds, Dried Dates and Coconut.","Almonds, Coconut, Cocoa Powder, _Dry Dates, Fennel, Sugar, Wheat Flour, _Artificial Flavours & Food Colours (E-171), _(E-102), (E-110), (E-133), (E-127).","","assets/images/products/mouth_freshener/arabic/arabic10.png","assets/images/products/mouth_freshener/nutrition/nutrition10.png"),A.b_(11,71,"A stronger, more minty version of the original Shahi Deluxe.","Fennel Seeds, Betelnuts, Dry Dates, _Cardamom, N.N Sweetener (Saccharin) _and Artificial Flavors.","","assets/images/products/mouth_freshener/arabic/arabic11.png",""),A.b_(12,72,"A childhood favorite, sugar coated fennel seeds.","Fennel Seeds, Glucose, Wheat Flour, _Food Colors (Tatrazine Yellow E-102 _Brilliant Blue E-133, Erythrosine E-127 _Titanium Dioxide E-171 Sunset Yellow E-110).","","assets/images/products/mouth_freshener/arabic/arabic12.png","assets/images/products/mouth_freshener/nutrition/nutrition12.png")],t.nJ))
